Oh, I didn't know you were on this shift. Proverbial bad penny.

400
00:31:01,274 --> 00:31:02,530
晚餐吃什么?
What's for dinner?

401
00:31:02,554 --> 00:31:04,650
希望不是又做了那种慢炖羊肉。
I hope it's not that slow-cooked lamb thing again.

402
00:31:04,674 --> 00:31:06,370
吐司上的屎，对吧?
Shite on toast, will that do you?

403
00:31:06,394 --> 00:31:07,930
我跟你说……
I tell you what...

404
00:31:07,954 --> 00:31:09,650
好好看看这张英俊的脸。
Take a good look at this handsome face.

405
00:31:09,674 --> 00:31:11,330
你可能很快就看不到了。
You might not be seeing it much longer.

406
00:31:11,354 --> 00:31:14,074
是啊，你中彩票了?可能是吧。
Oh, yeah, you won the lottery, then? Could be.

407
00:31:39,434 --> 00:31:41,474
