Aye, you're right.

408
00:31:45,514 --> 00:31:47,490
我也是认真的。
And I'm serious, as well.

409
00:31:47,514 --> 00:31:49,330
看不见你。
Aye.

410
00:31:49,354 --> 00:31:51,794
