Well, that's your choice, but you'll regret it.

411
00:31:53,274 --> 00:31:54,730
你还好吗?
You OK?

412
00:31:54,754 --> 00:31:57,514
当然，不用担心。好。
Aye, sure, no worries. Good.

413
00:32:10,514 --> 00:32:12,130
你在这里做什么?
What are you doing here?

414
00:32:12,154 --> 00:32:14,570
你不是应该在费尔岛吗?
Shouldn't you be in Fair Isle?

415
00:32:14,594 --> 00:32:17,050
怎么，你没听说过亚历克斯·加尔布雷斯吗?
What, you not heard about Alex Galbraith?

416
00:32:17,074 --> 00:32:18,490
嗯,我听说过。
Well, I heard.

417
00:32:18,514 --> 00:32:22,490
我以为你会待久一点。凯西要带我爸爸来
I just thought you'd stay longer. Cassie is bringing my dad

418
00:32:22,514 --> 00:32:24,634
