He's been sitting there since we got back.

444
00:34:11,274 --> 00:34:12,970
爸爸。
Dad.

445
00:34:12,994 --> 00:34:14,194
我有吃的。
I got some food.

446
00:34:16,914 --> 00:34:18,634
