They want me back at work.

448
00:34:21,994 --> 00:34:23,354
我明早得走了。
I have to go in the morning.

449
00:34:24,554 --> 00:34:26,170
当然可以。
Of course.

450
00:34:26,194 --> 00:34:28,554
别为我们担心，我们会没事的。
Don't you worry about us, we're going to be fine.

451
00:34:52,434 --> 00:34:55,570
